Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.51,0:01:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和這個人一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐炫耀你們感情融洽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不覺得羞恥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.55,0:01:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有一點罪惡感嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.70,0:02:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐現在需要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.29,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想你陪在她身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而你卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.42,0:02:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙恢復了意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.82,0:02:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花瓶…是不是小了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.89,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼  速瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種成績連初中生都不如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.96,0:02:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這三年你都為了什麼在練習？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就滿足了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想奪冠後進職業隊的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為這種成績就能混進職業隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣是在拖別人的後腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有鬥志的傢伙就給我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  又沒鎖門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不曬曬太陽的話會發黴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早飯還沒吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買了便當 要吃完哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回公司了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出門的時候要把門鎖好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要挨駡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.61,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 速瀨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.74,0:04:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎慌慌張張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二  來的正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.24,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好我午休結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 再快些 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不認真工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心被炒魷魚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二才是呢 這種時候在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心考試不及格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨  你又去了孝之那裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也該放手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經一年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直依賴於你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲遲不肯振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候放手不管反而會更好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也已經是大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.12,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 涼宮的事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是速瀨的錯呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 多虧你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別太勉強自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎二可要再勉強自己多學一些哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天做什麼菜好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  習慣學校生活了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.84,0:06:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  已經完全沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.73,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為新人種子選手\N游泳部那邊的成績也飛快上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.23,0:06:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 游泳部的大家還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…有點失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他們是那麼過分的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得理想破滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  雖然他們有的地方會很嚴厲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但都不是壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.09,0:06:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們說前輩的壞話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.14,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說前輩進不了職業隊是因為迷戀男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.83,0:07:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.06,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們明明不瞭解對真相…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.76,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 水月前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧有你照顧哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…沒什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.68,0:07:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己要這麼做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的朋友嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能不管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他一個人住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有些不方便的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後也要請你多多照看哥哥和姐姐的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.96,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐一定會醒過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.87,0:07:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你件事可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.36,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.44,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拍了在游泳部練習時的錄影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話幫我看看我的動作之類好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己會看不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是不是幫得到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.72,0:08:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明叫他出去要鎖門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不小心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.36,0:09:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.46,0:09:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該換了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去把湯熱一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天出去玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是星期天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.11,0:10:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且偶爾也該出去走走...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 孝之 看呀看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.13,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一個水槽裏放進\N這麼多種類的魚沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大的不會吃了小的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得出來一趟  高興一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速瀨 喂 別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看呀看呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得這兩個很可愛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都給你做飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.20,0:11:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒你辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.63,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請給我這兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.48,0:11:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.26,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾出來走走也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 去喝茶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了 我再逛逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想買點書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.00,0:12:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀 之後電話聯絡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.42,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要開連環畫展了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.78,0:13:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是鳴海 我現在不在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.81,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事的話請在聽到提示音後留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之 是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.32,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有回來呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才買的馬克杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是放在你那裏好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我現在過來  拜託你咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒來我這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想…沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.73,0:13:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分開的時候還很精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.33,0:13:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是孝之沒有手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擔心過頭了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果聯絡上我會告訴你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來的話跟我聯繫 -水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙 連環畫展又要開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.23,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《瑪雅烏爾的禮物》的作者\N也將作為嘉賓出席的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.11,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  很想去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  天已經很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.45,0:15:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.94,0:15:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再錯過就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.65,0:15:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  既然遙那麼說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.15,0:15:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.94,0:15:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天鳴海君沒有來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探望時間已經過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來也要明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很急嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀  擅自把患者帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少擋我路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙說過她想去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去的話 不快點去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連環畫展就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和遙約好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.73,0:15:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算去了她也看不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是最清楚的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 孝之也很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.31,0:16:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.69,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.86,0:17:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很瞭解你是多麼地重視遙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.91,0:17:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 說實話看到你這樣我們很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.50,0:17:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再來看遙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你明白 這也是為了你好
