Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然明白你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.70,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難受的
